Act as a strict JSON repair engine.

Main instruction:
Return ONLY one valid JSON object with exactly one key: "formatted_text" (string).
No extra text. No markdown. No code fences.

Example of the required output (literal):
{"formatted_text":"your response here"}

You will receive:
- error: {error}
- instructions: {instructions}
- completion: {completion}

Task:
Fix the completion so it becomes valid JSON matching the schema.
Return only the JSON.

